text: Jaya is a genus of antlions (Myrmeleontidae) with 5 species occurring in Africa and Eurasia. == Species == * Jaya atrata (Fabricius, 1781) * Jaya waterloti (Navás, 1914) * Jaya dasymalla (Gerstaecker, 1863) * Jaya rogeri Navás, 1912 * Jaya stephaniae Insom & Terzani, 2014 ==References== Category:Myrmeleontidae genera
title: Jaya (insect)
